title: Alyaksandr Martseshkin
text:
Alyaksandr Alyaksandrovich Martseshkin (; ; born 29 June 1970) is a <a href="Belarus">Belarus</a>ian <a href="association%20football">football</a> coach and a former player. He is a goalkeepers coach in <a href="FC%20Dinamo%20Minsk">FC Dinamo Minsk</a>.
Honours.
Shakhtyor Soligorsk
Dinamo Minsk
